{"TopicId":154156,"ForumId":32,"TopicTitle":"How long is a Kerbin year?","CreatedByName":"pincushionman","CreatedById":98495,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-12-29T06:34:32Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"pincushionman","CreatedById":98495,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-12-29T06:34:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ve been working on an orrery for the Kerbol system and I\u0027ve run into a couple of issues with regard to the length of Kerbin\u0027s year.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUsing values from the wiki and extracted from the game (suppposedly) using HyperEdit, I\u0027ve managed to calculate this year length:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ctable border=\u00221\u0022 cellpadding=\u00220\u0022 cellspacing=\u00220\u0022 style=\u0022height:402px;border-collapse:collapse;border:medium none;\u0022 width=\u0022655\u0022\u003E\u003Ctbody\u003E\u003Ctr\u003E\u003Ctd style=\u0022width:152.75pt;border:solid 1pt;padding:0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt;\u0022 valign=\u0022top\u0022 width=\u0022204\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:normal;\u0022\u003E\nParameter\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/td\u003E\n\u003Ctd style=\u0022width:45pt;border:solid 1pt;border-left:none;padding:0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt;\u0022 valign=\u0022top\u0022 width=\u002260\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:normal;\u0022\u003E\nSymbol\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/td\u003E\n\u003Ctd style=\u0022width:148pt;border:solid 1pt;border-left:none;padding:0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt;\u0022 valign=\u0022top\u0022 width=\u0022197\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:normal;\u0022\u003E\nValue\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/td\u003E\n\u003Ctd style=\u0022border:solid 1pt;border-left:none;padding:0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt;\u0022 valign=\u0022top\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:normal;\u0022\u003E\nSource\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/td\u00